{"tid":2026743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】新木優子氣質超越迪麗熱巴　IG齋靠樣勁吸400萬粉絲","createTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T06:12:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b55d00b8bbd61e3839957635782c8b0655b6822","tid":2026743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:00.000Z","msg":"現年27歲的日本文青女神新木優子憑精美的五官、清新脫俗的氣質早在小學時期已經被星探發掘，從此深得大眾喜愛，成為不少男士心中的理想女神，在Instagram坐擁近390萬粉絲，最近更打敗新垣結衣成為「日職球員票選至愛女藝人」第一名。新木優子樣子與迪麗熱巴有幾分相似，甚至多出幾分氣質，早前推出寫真集反應熱烈，之後又為多本雜誌拍攝內頁，大曬美貌及長腿，又不時在個人IG分享美照。"},{"pid":"10d9b69998b52e2b681372ed7bbfa6a6bc8af8ef","tid":2026743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200520/339900830033514496.jpeg/_wlwdFRCSOAuIohNkOETk9nJFajhysAEOyejEDsnoxA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200520%2F339900830033514496.jpeg%2F_wlwdFRCSOAuIohNkOETk9nJFajhysAEOyejEDsnoxA&h=85fc7d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200520/339900832021614592.jpeg/4k_MThHi_clGix_g3bx2HmVqpWSJmGHgWOFRcFjhUXA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200520%2F339900832021614592.jpeg%2F4k_MThHi_clGix_g3bx2HmVqpWSJmGHgWOFRcFjhUXA&h=257471e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200520/339900833787416576.jpeg/uO70QaAfskONgXsqAkhDbBkXnc6VuFvYfNKulHzSrpQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200520%2F339900833787416576.jpeg%2FuO70QaAfskONgXsqAkhDbBkXnc6VuFvYfNKulHzSrpQ&h=52784644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06aaf8f5d07c2f8a4f4704845620ee9ede8dce09","tid":2026743,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200